What to do with leftover egg yolks? Yesterday my friend, Rina suggested doing LEMON CURD and she is so nice, even sent some recipes to me. I picked up 1 from https://www.lifeloveandsugar.com but I didn't follow exactly. ⁣
⁣⁣
⁣
⁣⁣
⁣⁣ Ingredients: ⁣⁣
🍋 Fresh lemon juice from 1 lemon⁣
🍋 Finely grated lemon zest⁣
🍋 20g lakanto⁣
🍋 3 egg yolks (Leftover yolks from making buns) ⁣
🍋 3.5 thick slices of butter⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
Instructions:⁣
➡️ Combine everything in a metal bowl over a pot of simmering water. ⁣
➡️ Whisking constantly till mixture thickens. ⁣
➡️ Let it cool and pour into a container. ⁣
➡️ Keep in the fridge and best to consume within 1-2 weeks. ⁣
⁣⁣
